etica, clean, sans-serif, Regular, ËÎÌå; font-size: 12px; line-height: 30px; \\" mce_style=\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: #666666; font-family: arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif, Regular, ËÎÌå; font-size: 12px; line-height: 30px; \\">5、 可能在运输过程中，由于不可抗力造成延迟。</p><p style=\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif, Regular, ËÎÌå; font-size: 12px; line-height: 30px; \\" mce_style=\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: #666666; font-family: arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif, Regular, ËÎÌå; font-size: 12px; line-height: 30px; \\">发生这种情况，您可以通过我们的售后服务热线 010-62159910查询货品情况。</p><p style=\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif, Regular, ËÎÌå; font-size: 12px; line-height: 30px; \\" mce_style=\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: #666666; font-family: arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif, Regular, ËÎÌå; font-size: 12px; line-height: 30px; \\"><br></p><p></p>', NULL, 1, '', 0, 0, '2011-10-12 22:59:33', 1, '2011-10-13 10:18:02', 4, 1, 0, 1, 1, 'page', 0);
