lor: initial; vertical-align: top; \\"></font></em><font color=\\"#0000ff\\"> <strong style=\\"font-weight: 700; \\">FaceTime 与 Address Book</strong> </font></font></li><li style=\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; list-style-type: disc; list-style-position: outside; list-style-image: initial; \\"><font color=\\"#0000ff\\"><font size=\\"2\\"><em style=\\"font-style: italic; \\"><img border=\\"0\\" alt=\\"按此在新窗口浏览图片\\" src=\\"http://www.apple.com.cn/macbookpro/images/facetime_thumbs_ios20110224.jpg\\" style=\\"border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; vertical-align: top; \\"></em> <strong style=\\"font-weight: 700; \\">与 iOS 装置进行 FaceTime 通话</strong> </font></font></li></ul></div><p style=\\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.12em; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; line-height: 1.4; \\"><br><br><br><font size=\\"2\\"><font color=\\"#800080\\"><img border=\\"0\\" alt=\\"按此在新窗口浏览图片\\" src=\\"http://www.apple.com.cn/macbookpro/images/features_trackpad20110224.jpg\\" style=\\"border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; vertical-align: top; float: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; \\"></font> </font></p><p style=\\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.12em; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; line-height: 1.4; \\"><font size=\\"2\\">Multi-Touch 触控板，<br>不能不染指。Multi-Touch 触控板是你与屏幕内容进行互动的最自然的方式，平滑的玻璃表面给你宽裕的空间进行手势操作。</font></p><p style=\\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.12em; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; paddin